message.content:
Search for any PNG images related to molds in the project. Check these locations:
1. List all files in /tmp/docx_images/ recursively
2. List all PNG files matching mol-* or EP* or PC* or EB* patterns in public/assets/img/products/
3. Check for any PNG files in a "Productos/moldes/" directory or similar
4. Search for any recently added .png files anywhere in the project that might be mold-related

Report all findings with full paths and file sizes.

content.text: I'll search for mold-related PNG images across all the specified locations in parallel.

input.command: find "c:/Users/V/Documents/GitHub/Pagiweb2/public/assets/img/products/" -type f -iname "mol-*" -o -iname "EP*" -o -iname "PC*" -o -iname "EB*" 2>/dev/null | while read f; do echo "$(stat --printf='%s' "$f" 2>/dev/null || wc -c < "$f") $f"; done
input.description: List PNG files matching mol-*, EP*, PC*, EB* patterns in products dir
Check for moldes directories and PNG files within them
